1. What's the game about?
Basically, you are to guess the number the system guesses and input it. 
If you guess correctly, you will be assigned 10 points and then proceed to the next level. 
Otherwise, you will be assigned 0 point. You will be allowed to try 2 more times before it's game over.
There are 10 levels in this game and the level of difficulty increases as you increase in level.

2. REPLIT URL
